  <div class="spine-prose">
    <header class="page-head">
      <p class="eyebrow"><a href="/">CATALOGUE</a> / REFUNDS</p>
      <h1>Refunds.</h1>
    </header>
    <article class="prose">
      <p class="lede">
        ncert.oriz.in does not sell anything. There is no checkout, no payment
        gateway, no transaction. Consequently, <strong>no refunds apply</strong>.
      </p>
      <p>
        If you believe you were charged by someone claiming to represent
        ncert.oriz.in or oriz, please <a href="/contact/">contact us</a> —
        that would be fraud and we want to know about it.
      </p>
    </article>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
